:: "Everything is fine" {"position":"600,1025","size":"100,100"}
=><=

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["It was routine" ], you tell yourself. It's a Friday night, people get fucked up and drive home. 

People get stopped all the time. Good, bad or indifferent.

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["People get stopped allllll the time " ]

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Alll the time..."]

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Alll the time..."] you whisper, eyes darting to the mirrors as you drive away

[["Just keep fucking going"->event3]]




:: "What if I've fucked everything?" {"position":"725,1025","size":"100,100"}
=><=
(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["You've fucked your sister over, WHY DID YOU HESISTATE? THEY'RE ALL GONNA FIGURE IT OUT SOME DAY!"]

You inhale quickly as if you've been caught, staring hard into the heat. 


(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Take it easy it babe"]


You feel the sweat beading on your forehead, your tummy beginning to churn. 

[["Just gotta keep going"->event3]]




:: Ask what this is about {"position":"600,600","size":"100,100"}
  =><=
  
  (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
  
  |player>["“Is there a reason I’ve been stopped?” ]  you ask, hands tight on the wheel. 
  
You mentally face palm.
(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
  |player>["As if he's gonna tell you” ] 
  
  

The officer straightens, studying you for a moment before repeating the request, slower this time.

You smile softly and hand over your license. After a brief check, they return it without comment and motion for you to move along.


  =><=

[[Continue driving? ->event2]]





:: Call Mama {"position":"475,1025","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You dial Mama's number, she always knows what to say.

[[Listen to Mama's voice->event3]]




:: Call for help {"position":"550,1450","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You pull your phone out and call RACV. 

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["This still counts as lying low..." ]

As you wait, the reality of being stuck settles in.

Whatever happens next, it won’t be on your time.

[[Wait->outro]]




:: Get out of the car {"position":"600,1325","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You inspect the damage and quite frankly, you don't know what you're looking at. All you know is that the tires fucked and you have no spare. 

Opening the door, you slump back into the drivers seat, hazards blinking

The road is empty in both directions.

Officers about 15km from where you came...

and the next best stop is another 30...


[[Call for help]]
[[Try to handle it yourself]]




