:: Light a cigarette? {"position":"600,900","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You take a deep drag, exhaling through your nose, trying to make sense of what happened.


[["Everything is fine"]] 

[["What if I've fucked everything?"]] 

[[Call Mama]] 





:: Reach for your wallet {"position":"725,600","size":"100,100"}
  =><=

You comply, avoiding eye contact with the officer. 

You reach into your bag for your wallet. As you take it out, something slips and lands against the seat — a bracelet you recognize instantly. 

*"Shit"*

The officer’s gaze lingers for a moment as you open your wallet, and hand the piece of plastic to them, eyes fixed to the dotted lines ahead. 


The officer swiftly hands it back and waves you forward.


[[Continue driving? ->event2]]




:: Try to handle it yourself {"position":"675,1450","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You stare harder at the wheel and back bumpers as if the solution would hit you on the head. The sun is setting and damage is worse than you hoped.

You’re not going anywhere anytime soon.

[[Continue->outro]]




