(set: $name to (prompt: [Your name, please:], "Frances Spayne", "Don't care", "Confirm"))


:: event1 {"position":"600,450","size":"100,100"}
  =><=

You finally see another human being but you immediately want to turn around. Traffic slows suddenly, funneling cars into a narrow lane marked by cones and signs you don't want to see.


(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Oh, fuck me, man."]

A transportation officer steps forward and gestures for you to pull over. 

You pull over, exhaling slowly as you come to a stop. 

Rolling the window down, they approach your car...

(enchant:?officer, (text-style:"italic"))
|officer>["...Good evening ma'am, just after your drivers license please."]


[[Ask what this is about]]
[[Reach for your wallet]]




:: event2 {"position":"600,775","size":"100,100"}
=><=

The checkpoint disappears in your rearview mirror, but your grip on the wheel doesn’t loosen.

You replay the interaction in your head. 

The officer’s tone.

The way they looked at you. 


 (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
  
  |player>["He knew who I was...didn't he?"] 


If something goes wrong, it won’t just affect you...

[[Light a cigarette?]]





:: event3 {"position":"600,1200","size":"100,100"}
=><=

As you flick the butt out the window, the sound comes without warning.

A sharp bang, the steering wheel jerking in your hands. Tears spring to your eyes.


Fear.

Exhaustion.


You try to keep it together but you can't even keep the car on the road. 

You fight the car into the emergency stopping lane as you hear the rubber flapping.


Everything comes to a stop and you lick the tears from your lips. 

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["I can't do this..." ]

[[Get out of the car]]




:: introduction {"position":"550,275","size":"100,100"}
=><=
 ###nothing out of the ordinary 
The neverending road stretches ahead of you, 100kms of absolute nothing, knuckles whitening at the wheel. You keep the air con blasting on your fingertips to keep you awake. 

It’s been days since you last heard from your sister, Mufudzi, and her last message still echoes in your head. 

(enchant:?Mufudzi, (text-style:"italic"))

|Mufudzi>[ "For the better..."

"For the better...."

"For the better....."]


She said she was safe. That you would see her soon, lay low...

...And to not tell a soul.


You want to believe her — even if nothing about her disappearance feels right.

She said it would all make sense soon. “For the better,” she promised.

---

 
[[Keep driving ->event1]]

(enchant: ?passage's chars, via (t8n-delay:pos * 45) + (t8n:'instant'))


:: outro {"position":"600,1600","size":"100,100"}
=><=

The road is quiet again.

Somewhere ahead, your sister is waiting.

For now, all you can do is sit with the choices you’ve made — and just pray they were the right ones.

  (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Oh Mufudzi, what did you get yourself into?"]



